(857, 0, 'Shapechanger', 'trait', NULL, 'monsters', '{\"tag\": \"trait0\", \"name\": \"Shapechanger\", \"type\": \"trait\", \"priority\": \"10\", \"description\": \"[Name] can use [their] action to polymorph into a [sizegreater] bear-humanoid hybrid or into a [sizegreater] bear, or back into [their] true form, which is humanoid. [Their] statistics, other than [their] size and AC, are the same in each form. Any equipment [they] is wearing or carrying isn\'t transformed. [They] reverts to [their] true form if [they] dies.\"}'),
