(1292, 0, 'Channel Divinity', 'action', NULL, 'classes', '{\"tag\": \"action3\", \"name\": \"Channel Divinity\", \"type\": \"action\", \"values\": [{\"name\": \"value1\", \"type\": \"DC Wisdom\", \"expression\": \"8+PROF+WIS\"}, {\"name\": \"value2\", \"type\": \"-st-nd-rd\", \"expression\": \"(((LVL-1)/3)<6)*((LVL-1)/3) + (((LVL-1)/3)>5)*5\"}], \"charges\": \"1 + (LVL>5) + (LVL>17)\", \"levelMax\": \"7\", \"levelMin\": \"5\", \"priority\": \"25\", \"recharge\": \"short\", \"description\": \"[Name] channels divine energy directly from [their] deity, using that energy to fuel the following magical effects:\\n- _Turn Undead_: [name] presents [their] holy symbol and speak a prayer censuring the undead. Each undead that can see or hear [them] within 30 feet must make a {value1} saving throw. When an undead fails its saving throw, it is instantly destroyed if its challenge rating is 1/2 or lower. If an undead of higher challenge rating fails its saving throw, it is turned for 1 minute or until it takes any damage. \\n- _Reaper_: when [name] casts a necromancy spell of {value2} level of lower that normally targets only one creature, the spell can instead target two creatures within range and within 5 feet of each other\\n\\n\"}'),
