(1568, 0, 'Revelation in Flesh', 'bonus', NULL, 'classes', '{\"tag\": \"bonus4\", \"name\": \"Revelation in Flesh\", \"type\": \"bonus\", \"levelMin\": \"14\", \"priority\": \"25\", \"description\": \"[Name] unleashes the aberrant truth hidden within [them]self. [Name] gains one of the following benefits:\\n- [Their] body, along with any equipment [they] is wearing or carrying, becomes slimy and pliable. [They] can move through any space as narrow as 1 inch without squeezing, and [they] can spend 5 feet of movement to escape from nonmagical restraints or being grappled.\\n-[They] gains a swimming speed equal to twice [their] walking speed, and [they] can breathe underwater. Moreover, gills grow from [their] neck or fan out from behind [their] ears, [their] fingers become webbed, or [they] grow writhing cilia that extend through [their] clothing.\\n- [They] gains a flying speed equal to [their] walking speed and can hover. As [they] fly, [their] skin glistens with mucus or shines with an otherworldly light.\\n- [They] can see any invisible creature within 60 feet of [them], provided it isn\'t behind total cover. [Their] eyes also turn black or become writhing sensory tendrils.\\n\\n\\n\"}'),
