(1632, 0, 'Book of Shadows', 'trait', NULL, 'classes', '{\"tag\": \"trait3\", \"name\": \"Book of Shadows\", \"type\": \"trait\", \"levelMax\": \"8\", \"levelMin\": \"5\", \"priority\": \"20\", \"description\": \"[Name] has found a old grimoire written in a lost language. This book contains encrypted  knowledge passed from [patron] to those who came before [name], and [they] is desperately trying to decipher it. By studying this book [name] has so far acquired these powers:\\n- [Name] no longer needs to sleep and can\'t be forced to sleep by any means.\\n- [Name] can cast [their] 1st level spells as rituals without expending spell slots.\\n- If a creature writes its name on a page of the book, [name] can write in the same page a message to that creature at any time. The creature hears the message in its mind and, if it replies, its message appears on the page. The writing disappears after 1 minute.\\n- If [name] loses the book, [they] can perform a 1-hour ceremony to summon it.\\n\"}'),
